description: The lesser horseshoe bat was found in the cellar of a home in the south of the island, experts said.
title: Lesser horseshoe bat species found on Isle of Man for first time
title_page: Lesser horseshoe bat species found on Isle of Man for first time - BBC News
maintext: A suspected sighting was made on the island in 2006, two miles from the site of the recent discovery, but it flew away before it could be verified.
